# Phase 1 Remediation Rule

When Phase 1 validation fails (typecheck, build, test, lint, contracts, Docker, smoke tests):

1. Read [`ai-agents/phase-1/phase-1-remediation-agent.md`](ai-agents/phase-1/phase-1-remediation-agent.md)
2. Use skill [`.cursor/skills/stream-heaven/phase-1/phase-1-remediation-agent/basic/SKILL.md`](.cursor/skills/stream-heaven/phase-1/phase-1-remediation-agent/basic/SKILL.md) for single-service fixes
3. Use [advanced skill](.cursor/skills/stream-heaven/phase-1/phase-1-remediation-agent/advanced/SKILL.md) for full autonomous loops
4. Run `pnpm run phase1:remediate` before handoff

Do not regenerate agents with `generate-agents.mjs`. Apply smallest correct diffs only.
